| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1020 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fc21e7cb-2438-51e5-acfc-b551a6bf5aa2"
